data.description: A must see! This fully renovated, turn-key home offers an oasis of modern living, is located in the highly desirable Beavercreek school district, and is just minutes from WPAFB. With over $70,000 in renovations and upgrades, there’s nothing that’s been untouched in this home. Updates include new water heater (2023), new carpet and vinyl flooring (2023), brand new energy efficient windows (2021), custom blinds (2021), new water softener (2020), newer roof (2019), and smart home features like fingerprint enabled locks and smart thermostat (2022), to name a few. As you step inside, you’re greeted with soaring 18ft vaulted ceilings in the living room and tons of natural light. The beautifully updated kitchen includes brand new quartz countertops (2023) and all new stainless-steel appliances (2021). The first-floor master bedroom provides privacy and includes a walk-in closet and a spa-like on-suite full bath. Two additional bedrooms, a second full bath, and lots of closet space are located on the second floor. And you can’t miss the inviting and comfortable ambiance of the back patio and sprawling backyard. The clubhouse, tennis courts, and sparkling pools are just steps away, providing endless recreational opportunities. And the HOA takes care of lawn maintenance and snow removal, allowing you to enjoy the community amenities hassle-free. Don't miss out on this exceptional property – schedule a viewing today!
